'''旅行者錦標賽'''（Travelers Championship）是美國[[高爾夫球|高爾夫球]][[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]的一個賽事。旅行者錦標賽在康格涅狄克州舉行。2016賽季的旅行者錦標賽將改在8月分的第一個禮拜舉行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pgatour.com/news/2015/07/23/travelers-championship-new-date.html |title=Travelers Championship announces new date |publisher=PGA Tour |date=July 23, 2015 |first=Brian |last=Wacker |access-date=2016-02-24 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108101911/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2015/07/23/travelers-championship-new-date.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。旅行者錦標賽開始於1952年<ref name=tkwft>{{cite news |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8M8wAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8d0FAAAAIBAJ&pg=5992,222283 |title=Ted Kroll wins first tournament |newspaper=Ottawa Citizen |agency=Associated Press |date=September 2, 1952 |page=18}}</ref>。

